      </layout>
   </head>
   <body xml:id="thebody" style="defaultCaption">
      <div xml:lang="en">
         <p begin="00:00:01.93" end="00:00:04.93" region="speaker">The Clause Inclusion and Flow Down section contains</p>
         <p begin="00:00:04.93" end="00:00:08.00" region="speaker">the assurance that all subcontracts in excess of</p>
         <p begin="00:00:08.00" end="00:00:14.03" region="speaker">$650,000 ($1,500,000 for construction) adopt a plan</p>
         <p begin="00:00:14.03" end="00:00:16.13" region="speaker">which offers further subcontracting</p>
         <p begin="00:00:16.13" end="00:00:17.93" region="speaker">opportunities.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:17.93" end="00:00:20.63" region="speaker">You must agree to this by checking the box then</p>
         <p begin="00:00:20.63" end="00:00:22.63" region="speaker">click &quot;Save and Continue.&quot;</p>
    </div>
